//www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/458409796168229288/comments/default/7039325410660108866?v=2"},{"rel":"self","type":"application/atom+xml","href":"https://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/458409796168229288/comments/default/7039325410660108866?v=2"},{"rel":"alternate","type":"text/html","href":"https://program-think.blogspot.com/2010/06/howto-prevent-hacker-attack-3.html?showComment=1306481408111#c7039325410660108866","title":"如何防止黑客入侵[3]&#65306;如何构造安全的口令/密码"}],"author":[{"name":{"$t":"编程随想"},"uri":{"$t":"https://www.blogger.com/profile/11741356469378252621"},"email":{"$t":"noreply@blogger.com"},"gd$image":{"rel":"http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#thumbnail","width":"26","height":"32","src":"https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-GTIh2pdzDYI/VtcrB6rX0pI/AAAAAAAABUg/vWdDxEU4N6c/s220/Thinker.jpg?cache=36c4cca294ae50025f1c139a5907df5d"}}],"thr$in-reply-to":{"xmlns$thr":"http://purl.org/syndication/thread/1.0","href":"https://program-think.blogspot.com/2010/06/howto-prevent-hacker-attack-3.html","ref":"tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-458409796168229288","source":"http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/posts/default/458409796168229288","type":"text/html"},"gd$extendedProperty":[{"name":"blogger.itemClass","value":"pid-1582521586"},{"name":"blogger.displayTime","value":"2011年5月27日 15:30:00"}]},{"gd$etag":"W/\"D0QNQHk_fyp7ImA9XxZbE0Q.\"","id":{"$t":"tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-3667080682497899841"},"published":{"$t":"2020-12-20T00:29:51.747+08:00"},"updated":{"$t":"2020-12-20T00:29:51.747+08:00"},"app$edited":{"xmlns$app":"http://www.w3.org/2007/app","$t":"2020-12-20T00:29:51.747+08:00"},"title":{"$t":"TO null（30楼）\n[b]关于“中美热战的可能性”[/b]\n在如下博文末尾，提到俺的观点：美国..."},"content":{"type":"html","$t":"TO null（30楼）<br />[b]关于“中美热战的可能性”[/b]<br />在如下博文末尾，提到俺的观点：美国佬不会主动进行热战，美国佬倾向于用【遏制战略】。<br />《[url=https://program-think.blogspot.com/2018/07/Forty-Years-of-China-USA-Relations.html]从量变到质变——中美关系40年[/url]》<br />该博文写于2018，从后续这几年的迹象来看，“遏制”的倾向很明显。<br /><br />对“热战”这个话题，比较危险的是【习呆呆】。<br />俺不止一次点评过，他有【楞头青】的倾向——年轻时被文革洗脑；（掌权后）政治及外交方面都不够成熟，个人野心又很大。<br /><br />天朝周边有好几个热点地区（台湾问题、中印边境纠纷、南海纠纷、钓鱼岛纠纷、北韩核问题）。如果包子在其中某个热点地区做出严重误判，可能会引发地区性热战。<br />一旦天朝先动手，美国佬就少了很多舆论方面的顾虑；而美国军界的很多人会倾向于把“地区性热战”扩大为“全面热战”。<br />（俺多次说过：天朝的很多人低估了美国军方的战争意志，包括打“全面核战”的战争意志）<br /><br />另，<br />这不是俺的危言耸听。基辛格在前几个月警告过：如今的局面与一战前的“英德矛盾”有相似之处。<br />言下之意，基辛格很担心如今的“中美对抗”演变为类似当年的一战（一战前，没有哪个大国想打一场全面战争，但最后却发展为全面战争）<br />顺便自吹一下：<br />在更早之前（从2019年初到今年），俺不止一次点评过：“习呆呆”与“威廉二世”（一战前的德国元首）的诸多相似之处（留言链接如下）<br />https://program-think.blogspot.com/2019/03/Why-Thinking-Hard-So-Hard.html?comment=1553425493037<br />https://program-think.blogspot.com/2019/11/POSIX-TUI-from-TTY-to-Shell-Programming.html?comment=1573548232223<br />https://program-think.blogspot.com/2020/04/Government-and-System-Robustness.html?comment=1588525080488"},"link":[{"rel":"edit","type":"application/atom+xml","href":"https://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/4975230973197205514/comments/default/3667080682497899841?v=2"},{"rel":"self","type":"application/atom+xml","href":"https://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/4975230973197205514/comments/default/3667080682497899841?v=2"},{"rel":"alternate","type":"text/html","href":"https://program-think.blogspot.com/2020/12/Study-and-Life.html?showComment=1608395391747#c3667080682497899841","title":"学习与人生&#8212;&#8212;700篇博文之感悟"},{"rel":"related","type":"application/atom+xml","href":"https://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/4975230973197205514/comments/default/2835895685199557733?v=2"}],"author":[{"name":{"$t":"编程随想"},"uri":{"$t":"https://www.blogger.com/profile/11741356469378252621"},"email":{"$t":"noreply@blogger.com"},"gd$image":{"rel":"http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#thumbnail","width":"26","height":"32","src":"https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-GTIh2pdzDYI/VtcrB6rX0pI/AAAAAAAABUg/vWdDxEU4N6c/s220/Thinker.jpg?cache=36c4cca294ae50025f1c139a5907df5d"}}],"thr$in-reply-to":{"xmlns$thr":"http://purl.org/syndication/thread/1.0","href":"http